---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Ghana Sector Deep Dives: Agriculture, Fintech, Real Estate, Healthcare"
  description="Ghana-specific sector intelligence. Not generic emerging market frameworks. Deep dives into agriculture, fintech, real estate, healthcare, logistics, and more."
  keywords="Ghana sectors, Ghana agriculture, Ghana fintech, Ghana real estate, Ghana healthcare, Ghana logistics, sector analysis Ghana"
>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-label">Sector Intelligence</div>
      <h1>Sector Deep Dives</h1>
      <p>Ghana-specific sector intelligence. Not generic emerging market frameworks. Each analysis includes market sizing, competitive dynamics, infrastructure requirements, and honest risk assessment.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="section reveal">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-label">Coming Soon</div>
        <div class="section-title">In the Pipeline</div>
        <div class="section-desc">Sector deep dives are being built with fresh cycle data through the v3.0 publishing pipeline. Each article passes 8 stages with 3 mandatory quality gates.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="article-card" style="opacity:0.65;">
          <span class="card-tag data">Sector</span>
          <h3>Agriculture: Beyond Cocoa</h3>
          <p>Cassava, shea, palm oil, poultry: where the real margins are. Updated with Hormuz fuel cost impact on agro-processing economics.</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="status-badge">In Pipeline</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="article-card" style="opacity:0.65;">
          <span class="card-tag data">Sector</span>
          <h3>Fintech Landscape 2026</h3>
          <p>Mobile money, digital lending, remittance corridors. Updated with BoG rate cut impact and diaspora legislation cluster.</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="status-badge">In Pipeline</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="article-card" style="opacity:0.65;">
          <span class="card-tag data">Sector</span>
          <h3>Real Estate: The Diaspora Trap</h3>
          <p>Why most diaspora real estate investments underperform. Land title risks, construction fraud, and what actually works.</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="status-badge">In Pipeline</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
